  "content": "<!--HTML--><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px;\">推特（Twitter&nbsp;/ X）作为一个全球性的社交平台，吸引了来自世界各地的大家，同时支持多种语言设置。成功登录推特后，界面默认语言一般为英文。对于中文大家来说，将推特界面设置为中文，有助于大大提升使用体验。接下来，这篇会手把手教您如何将推特X设置成中文，包括移动端和网页端的详细操作步骤。</span></p><h2><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">一、</span><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">推特X</strong><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">移动端</strong><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">APP如何</strong><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">设置中文</strong></span></h2><ol class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\"><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">打开推特应用</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">：首先，确保您的手机或平板上已安装推特应用。</span></p></li><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px;\">进入“设置和隐私”</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px;\">：点击左上角头像进入“设置”界面，然后点击“<strong>Settings and privacy</strong>”。<img src=\"/assets/images/files/twitter-app-change-language-1_$1729738908197025072_d8011694.png\" title=\"推特APP进入设置与隐私界面\" alt=\"推特APP进入设置与隐私界面\"/></span></p></li><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px;\">选择“语言”</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px;\">：在设置菜单中，找到并点击“<strong>Accessibility,display and languages</strong>”，然后选择<span style=\"font-family: Arial; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">“</span><strong>Languages</strong>”。</span></p></li><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px;\">更改语言</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px;\">：点击“<strong>P</strong><strong>referred language</strong>”，此界面下可以看到当前使用语言。 选择“<strong>Update language - Show more</strong>”，然后向下滑动语言列表中选择“中文（简体）”或“中文（繁体）”。<img src=\"/assets/images/files/twitter-app-change-language-2_$1729738916215087159_ef09470d.png\" title=\"推特APP设置中文语言\" alt=\"推特APP设置中文语言\"/></span></p></li><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">保存设置</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">：选择完毕后，推特应用将自动更新为中文界面。</span></p></li></ol><h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\">二、<strong>推特X</strong><strong>网页端</strong><strong>如何</strong><strong>设置中文</strong></span></h2><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><ol class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\"><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">登录推特账号</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">：在浏览器中打开推特官网，并登录你的账号。</span></p></li><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px;\">进入“设置和隐私”</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px;\">：在左侧选项栏中点击“<strong>More</strong>”，进入“<strong>Settings and privacy</strong>”。<img src=\"/assets/images/files/web-1_$1729677422614098857_4a89b024.jpg\" title=\"x网页端进入语言修改界面\" alt=\"x网页端进入语言修改界面\"/></span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px;\"></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">更改语言</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">：点击“</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Accessibility,display and languages</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">”，然后找到<span style=\"font-family: Arial; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">&quot;</span><strong>Languages</strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">&quot;</span>选项，选择&quot;<strong>Display language&quot;</strong>，点击下拉菜单，选择“<strong>中文（简体）</strong>”或“<strong>中文（繁体）</strong>”。<img src=\"/assets/images/files/web-3_$1729677775561044689_fa63e8f2.jpg\" title=\"x网页端设置中文\" alt=\"x网页端设置中文\"/></span></p></li><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">保存更改</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">：选择完毕后，点击页面底部的“保存”按钮。</span></p></li></ol><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">提示</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">：由于网络监管政策，国内大家想要访问推特，通常需要使用代理工具。移动端安卓大家想要下载X，需要先<a href=\"/article/411.html\">安装Google Play</a>等套件，而iOS大家则需要切换到</span><a href=\"/goods?id=ab_1578286983\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">外区</span>苹果ID</a><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">。对于国内大家来说确实非常麻烦，所以更加推荐大家使用网页端推特。另外，网页端和移动端设置并不互通，需要分别进行修改。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></p><h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\"><strong>老号吧：</strong><strong>一站式下载、</strong><strong><a href=\"/goods?id=ab_1578287018\">购买推特账号</a></strong></span></h2><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">如果不知道如何</span>下载推特<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">或者注册推特账号失败，老号吧能帮你解决这些问题。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></p><p><a href=\"/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">老号吧</span></a><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">（</span>老号吧<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">）是一个专业的账号购买平台，提供包括推特在内的多种社交媒体账号购买服务。该平台拥有以下优势：</span></span></p><ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\"><li><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">丰富的账号资源</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">：提供各种类型的推特账号，满足不同大家的需求。</span></span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">推特下载链接</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">：为</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">安卓大家</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">提供推特安装包下载链接。</span></span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">安全可靠</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">：所有账号均为真实且活跃，保证账号的稳定性和安全性。</span></span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">优质服务</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">：提供专业的客服支持，帮助大家解决购买和使用过程中的问题。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></span></p></li></ul><p><a href=\"/goods?id=ab_1578287018\"><img src=\"/assets/images/files/推特X账号购买_$1744167211337061395_7ec90f4e.png\" title=\"推特X账号购买\" alt=\"推特X账号购买\"/></a></p><h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\">三、<strong>推特中文设置的常见问题解答（FAQ）</strong></span></h2><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></p><h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold;\">1.&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">X设置中文失败怎么办？</span></strong></span></h3><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">如果你的推特界面没有中文选项，可能是因为账号注册地区不支持中文。可以尝试切换代理，<span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">移动端大家可以尝试清除应用缓存或重新安装X应用，以解决设置不生效的问题</span></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">，确保网络连接正常，避免因网络问题导致设置失败。如果<span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">以上方法均无法解决问题，可</span>联系X客服寻求帮助。</span></span></p><h3 style=\"margin-left: 0px; text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold;\">2.&nbsp;</span><a href=\"/article/387.html\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">推特怎么设置翻译中文</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">？</span></strong></span></h3><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">推特提供内置的翻译功能，在根据上文步骤设置好首选语言之后，在您想要翻译的推文下方，会看到“Translate Post”字样。除了内置翻译功能，如你使用的是网页端推特，推荐您在Chrome Web Store安装第三方翻译工具的插件，比如谷歌翻译，<a href=\"/article/480.html\">DeepL翻译</a>等。不同于内置翻译功能，第三方翻译插件支持翻译网页上任意选中的文字内容。</span></p><h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold;\">3.&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">如果我更改了语言，其他大家会看到什么语言的界面？</span></strong></span></h3><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">其他大家看到的界面语言取决于他们自己的语言设置，与您的设置无关。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">以上就是关于推特设置中文界面的所有教程，过程不复杂，只需按照上述步骤操作，就能轻松切换至中文界面。</span></p>",
